Use the following REST requests for configuring the Edge System, Edge Connectivity (including Modbus TCP connectivity and OPC UA connectivity), and storage.
	
The difference between the POST and the PUT method is that POST allows to create a configuration and PUT replaces a configuration. If you use POST on an existing configuration, the request will fail. 
